of $N$ segments of length $l$, modeled as a soft ellipsoid~\cite{murat-kremer1998}, 
is accurately approximated by the analytical form~\cite{eurich-maass2001}

prevtext:
The probability distribution for the shape of a freely-jointed polymer coil 
of $N$ segments of length $l$, modeled as a soft ellipsoid~\cite{murat-kremer1998}, 
